HELPING HANDS

Fighting managers aside, Balotelli has been involved in a few hand-outs. He donated money to his local church before allegedly roaming the streets of Manchester dressed as Santa Claus handing out free cash. Suarez famously handballed on the line to stop Ghana from scoring at the 2010 World Cup and also refused to shake Patrice Evra’s hand after being found guilty of racially abusing the French defender.

