T-SHIRT TROUBLES

Suarez and his Liverpool team-mates wore t-shirts of support (right) after he was banned for eight games for abusing Evra. While at Inter, Balotelli angered his own fans after wearing rivals AC Milan’s kit and he celebrated scoring in the Manchester derby with his ‘Why Always Me?’ t-shirt.

